\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33309,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/28\/best-believers-noble-parents\/","url_meta":{"origin":11983,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Parents: Best of believers serve their noble parents","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 28, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ka\u2019b ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was asked, \u201cWhich of the people is best?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cA believer in service of two noble parents.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r 160 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0643\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0628\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24120,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/12\/05\/prophet-fears-hawa-shahawat\/","url_meta":{"origin":11983,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Whims: The Prophet fears Muslims follow desires","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 5, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Barzah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, among what I fear most for you are seductive temptations in your appetites and your lusts, and the misguidance of whims.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 19787 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652